said sunday he was 78 
blitz died saturday night at cochin hospital following a serious 
illness the officials said the cause of death was not disclosed 
a belgianborn diamondcutter by trade blitz created club med 
in 1950 as a nonprofit association and led the first group of 
vacationers to a tent village in spains balearic islands 
club med villages progressed from tents to straw huts to modern 
hotel facilities prospering with a formula of completely prepaid 
notipping vacations in which clients pay with colored beads for 
the few extras like souvenirs or bar drinks 
with its image of sun sand and relaxation club med grew into 
one of the worlds largest tourism groups with more than 87000 
beds in its resorts 
