picassos 1905 selfportrait titled au lapin agile annenberg 
bought the picture in november after the exhibition opened in 
philadelphia last summer for 407 million the third most 
expensive artwork ever sold at auction 
vogel is proud of his invitations but doesnt take his work 
home the wall of his house he said are reserved for the drawings 
